+## 2026-03-12 Backend Optimize Phase 0 Priority Notes
+
+- Selected safe optimization order for the backend-optimize lane: `OPT-P1-001`, then `OPT-P1-002`, then `OPT-P1-003`, with `OPT-P1-004` kept as a fallback-path cleanup after the request-heavy booking and dashboard surfaces.
